AI-Driven Personalized Education Platform

📌 Project Overview

The AI-Driven Personalized Education Platform is designed to enhance learning experiences using AI. It provides customized learning plans, course recommendations, real-time chatbot assistance, and seamless WhatsApp alerts for learners.

🎯 Features

Personalized Learning Plans: AI-generated learning paths based on user preferences.

Course Catalog: Various courses covering AI, Machine Learning, Data Science, and Python.

AI Chatbot: 24/7 assistance to answer queries and guide users.

WhatsApp Alerts: Instant notifications and course details sent via WhatsApp.

User Progress Tracking: Monitors learning achievements.

Community Forum: A space for learners to interact and share knowledge.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (with FontAwesome for icons)

Backend: Python Flask

Database: SQLite / PostgreSQL (optional)

API Integration: WhatsApp API (for alerts)

🚀 Installation & Setup

Prerequisites

Ensure you have the following installed:

Python (>=3.8)

Flask

SQLite or PostgreSQL (for database)

Steps to Run Locally

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/Rahul200496/AI-DRIVEN-PERSONALISED-EDUCATION-PLATFORM..git
cd ai-edu-platform

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the Flask server:

python app.py

Open your browser and visit:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/

📡 Deployment

You can deploy this project using Heroku, AWS, or Vercel.

📄 API Endpoints

/ - Home Page

/courses - Courses List

/personalized_plan - AI-based Personalized Learning Plan

/chatbot - AI Chatbot

/whatsapp-alert - Send learning plans via WhatsApp

